body":"Wasn't she gonna tell everybody during the school's afternoon announcement, but Tsugumi rushed to stop her?","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":23,"motionName":"eeto01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":23,"voiceId":"event163-02-013","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":19}],"windowDisplayName":"Maya","body":"Yeah... I'm really glad Hazawa-san was there.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":19,"motionName":"smile03","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":19,"voiceId":"event163-02-014","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":16}],"windowDisplayName":"Aya","body":"So, how do you like being part of a music agency?","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":16,"motionName":"nf02","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":16,"voiceId":"event163-02-015","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":23}],"windowDisplayName":"Lisa","body":"Hmm~... We've just joined, so it still doesn't feel real~.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":23,"motionName":"nnf01","expressionName":"smile03","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":23,"voiceId":"event163-02-016","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":19}],"windowDisplayName":"Maya","body":"I know what you mean. I was the same way at first. But after working with an agency for a little bit, things start to feel different.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":19,"motionName":"smile03","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":19,"voiceId":"event163-02-017","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":1,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":0}],"windowDisplayName":"Haneoka Student","body":"U-um! Lisa-senpai...!","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":0,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[],"voices":[],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":23}],"windowDisplayName":"Lisa","body":"Hm? I've seen you at a lot of our shows...","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":23,"motionName":"nf03","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":23,"voiceId":"event163-02-018","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":0}],"windowDisplayName":"Haneoka Student","body":"I read about Roselia online! I'm so happy for you...!","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":0,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[],"voices":[],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":23}],"windowDisplayName":"Lisa","body":"Thank you~☆ We're gonna do our best to put on the coolest shows possible.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":23,"motionName":"smile02","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":23,"voiceId":"event163-02-019","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":0}],"windowDisplayName":"Haneoka Student","body":"I'll be there! Um, could I... shake your hand?","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[],"voices":[{"characterId":0,"voiceId":"#NAME?","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":23}],"windowDisplayName":"Lisa","body":"What?! I'm not famous or anything...","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":23,"motionName":"surprised01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":23,"voiceId":"event163-02-020","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":0}],"windowDisplayName":"Haneoka Student","body":"But you are! Signing with a music agency is a big deal, and I want to mark the occasion with a handshake!","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[],"voices":[{"characterId":0,"voiceId":"#NAME?","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":23}],"windowDisplayName":"Lisa","body":"Well, I guess when you put it like that~... Umm, okay. Is this good?","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":23,"motionName":"nnf02","expressionName":"smille03","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":23,"voiceId":"event163-02-021","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":0}],"windowDisplayName":"Haneoka Student","body":"Th-thank you! Goodbye...!","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[],"voices":[{"characterId":0,"voiceId":"#NAME?","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":1,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":16}],"windowDisplayName":"Aya","body":"Wow~! Her eyes were practically twinkling when she looked at you, Lisa-chan!","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":16,"motionName":"smile02","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":16,"voiceId":"event163-02-022","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":23}],"windowDisplayName":"Lisa","body":"Ahaha... That was a bit of a surprise. Phew, talk about intense.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":23,"motionName":"smile03","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":23,"voiceId":"event163-02-023","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":19}],"windowDisplayName":"Maya","body":"Fufu. It's been like that at school, too! Younger students are always coming to shake your hand during lunch.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":19,"motionName":"smile02","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":19,"voiceId":"event163-02-024","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":23}],"windowDisplayName":"Lisa","body":"Yeah, it's been happening a lot since that story was posted online~. But it's not like I've changed. This is all so weird.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":23,"motionName":"nf04","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":23,"voiceId":"event163-02-025","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":16}],"windowDisplayName":"Aya","body":"That's just how much everybody's rooting for Roselia!","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":16,"motionName":"smile01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":16,"voiceId":"event163-02-026","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":19}],"windowDisplayName":"Maya","body":"Has Roselia's debut concert been set yet?","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":19,"motionName":"nf02","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":19,"voiceId":"event163-02-027","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":23}],"windowDisplayName":"Lisa","body":"We're still waiting to hear about a date and a venue, but we've been told it'll be soon. Starting next week, we'll be busy with promo stuff.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":23,"motionName":"nf01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":23,"voiceId":"event163-02-028","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":16}],"windowDisplayName":"Aya","body":"Ah, us, too! We have a show next month, so we're promoting it now.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":16,"motionName":"nf05","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":16,"voiceId":"event163-02-029","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":23}],"windowDisplayName":"Lisa","body":"Oh, really? Actually, can I ask you two something...?","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":23,"motionName":"nf03","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":23,"voiceId":"event163-02-030","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":19}],"windowDisplayName":"Maya","body":"Sure. Hopefully, we'll have an answer for you.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":19,"motionName":"nf05","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":19,"voiceId":"event163-02-031","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":23}],"windowDisplayName":"Lisa","body":"This is our first time promoting our show with an agency, so we don't really have an idea of what to expect.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":23,"motionName":"nnf02","expressionName":"serious01","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":23,"voiceId":"event163-02-032","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":23}],"windowDisplayName":"Lisa","body":"It'd be nice to know if there was anything we should be careful about.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":23,"motionName":"eeto01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":23,"voiceId":"event163-02-033","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":16}],"windowDisplayName":"Aya","body":"Something to be careful about, huh? I-I'm not sure... Hmm~...","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":16,"motionName":"surprised01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":16,"voiceId":"event163-02-034","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":16}],"windowDisplayName":"Aya","body":"Ah! Greetings! Make sure you do them!","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":16,"motionName":"surprised01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":16,"voiceId":"event163-02-035","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":19}],"windowDisplayName":"Maya","body":"They are really important. Everything starts with a greeting and ends with a goodbye, after all.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":19,"motionName":"nf02","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":19,"voiceId":"event163-02-036","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":19}],"windowDisplayName":"Maya","body":"They show how courteous you are to the people you work with. We're also ready to greet every person who helps us at our shows.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":19,"motionName":"eeto01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":19,"voiceId":"event163-02-037","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":16}],"windowDisplayName":"Aya","body":"That's right! It's a sign of respect, but it makes people happy when they hear a nice cheerful greeting!","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":16,"motionName":"nf01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":16,"voiceId":"event163-02-038","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":16}],"windowDisplayName":"Aya","body":"They can also encourage those around you to give their all, and it can lighten up the mood around you. That's why greetings are really meaningful!","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":16,"motionName":"gattsu01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":16,"voiceId":"event163-02-039","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":23}],"windowDisplayName":"Lisa","body":"Wow~, I think I get what you're talking about.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":23,"motionName":"nf05","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":23,"voiceId":"event163-02-040","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":23}],"windowDisplayName":"Lisa","body":"When we have rehearsals, Ako gives these big cheerful greetings that always make me smile.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":23,"motionName":"nf02","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":23,"voiceId":"event163-02-041","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":19}],"windowDisplayName":"Maya","body":"Aya-san's greetings are great, too! The staff at our agency said they never fail to cheer them up when they're tired.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":19,"motionName":"smile02","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":19,"voiceId":"event163-02-042","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":16}],"windowDisplayName":"Aya","body":"Did they really say that?! Oh, I'm so happy~.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":16,"motionName":"smile02","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":16,"voiceId":"event163-02-043","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":23}],"windowDisplayName":"Lisa","body":"Fufu. I can imagine why. Aya's greetings brighten up the whole place.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":23,"motionName":"smile02","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":23,"voiceId":"event163-02-044","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":23}],"windowDisplayName":"Lisa","body":"Okay~. Greetings are a no-brainer, but they're really powerful, too~.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":23,"motionName":"nf04","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":23,"voiceId":"event163-02-045","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":16}],"windowDisplayName":"Aya","body":"And what else~...? Oh, communication is important too.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":16,"motionName":"eeto01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":16,"voiceId":"event163-02-046","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":23}],"windowDisplayName":"Lisa","body":"That makes sense. You need to let people know what's going on, as well as consult them when something comes up, right?","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":23,"motionName":"eeto01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":23,"voiceId":"event163-02-047","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":16}],"windowDisplayName":"Aya","body":"Right! When you join an agency, you and the agency work as a team, so it's best to always be communicating with each other.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[],"voices":[{"characterId":16,"voiceId":"event163-02-048","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":19}],"windowDisplayName":"Maya","body":"Everyone at the agency is thinking very hard about how to help us shine our brightest when we're on stage.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":19,"motionName":"nf01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":19,"voiceId":"event163-02-049","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":16}],"windowDisplayName":"Aya","body":"It's true! So you could cause a lot of trouble if you just do whatever you want without talking to the agency first.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":16,"motionName":"nf05","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":16,"voiceId":"event163-02-050","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":23}],"windowDisplayName":"Lisa","body":"You know... during our photo shoot, I saw lots of people from the agency making sure things went well.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":23,"motionName":"eeto01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":23,"voiceId":"event163-02-051","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":16}],"windowDisplayName":"Aya","body":"Right? That's why communication is important!","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":16,"motionName":"nf03","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":16,"voiceId":"event163-02-052","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":16}],"windowDisplayName":"Aya","body":"No matter how small it might be, if there's something on your mind, you should talk with your agency about it.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":16,"motionName":"nf05","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":16,"voiceId":"event163-02-053","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":23}],"windowD